{"tid":2236201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"乘客掏錢誤觸手槍　砰！運將見他胸口中彈淌血嚇壞了","createTime":"2020-10-09T09:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T10:17:44.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8240d466641da2022f0a05aa128f20abb80d8000","tid":2236201,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:57:26.000Z","msg":"北市一名陳姓男子前天（7日）上午搭乘計程車時，抵達基隆市時，他疑要將手伸進包內拿錢，不慎誤觸包內手槍板機-----<br />\n<br />\n據了解，前天上午8時許，30歲陳姓男子於台北市搭乘計程車，過程中，向計程車司機改變數次目的地，最後才決定前往基隆市中和路，快抵達時，陳姓男子將手伸進包內，不慎誤觸手槍板機，車內隨即傳出槍響，計程車司機回頭一看，發現陳姓男子胸口不斷流血，立刻將他送往醫院急救。<br />\n---------------<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n<br />\n經過院方搶救，陳姓男子撿回一命；警方在他的包內查獲2把手槍、子彈數顆，至於陳姓男子為何會誤觸手槍板機，警方已介入調查，並要追查槍枝來源。（突發中心戴之聖／基隆報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201009/RBSRKSOUQFAF3CL5JHBONTXXFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FRBSRKSOUQFAF3CL5JHBONTXXFQ%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=5903d70d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FRBSRKSOUQFAF3CL5JHBONTXXFQ%2F&h=e683e779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201009/RBSRKSOUQFAF3CL5JHBONTXXFQ/</a>"},{"pid":"2561b26e5e98e103e9061778295c5a46565e00ed","tid":2236201,"uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCoSZnb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCoSZnb.jpg&h=48bb268c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd29b2f5d0103697b14df0fef512e47dc0cf9d7c","tid":2236201,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2561b26e5e98e103e9061778295c5a46565e00ed","tid":2236201,"uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCoSZnb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCoSZnb.jpg&h=48bb